svg.text: Spud CMHC-8 on 02/28/17. Drill ahead f/69' with 26" bit and mud motor assembly.
Drill 26" hole to 523'. Run 16 jnts of 20", 19.12#, J-55, BUTT casing to a depth of 522'. Drill ahead with 17.5" bit w/Mud Motor and MWD.
Water added to pits,cooling mud. Clean temp In probe to verify accurate measure.
Pull to shoe to wipe the hole do some rig repairs, run to bottom, drill ahead.
Building too much angle, POH for new bit and tools.
Drill to 2056', pull out of hole to check bit. Bit and stabs bad: 1-2.5" out of gauge.
Drill 17.5" hole to 2934'. Pull tight coming out of hole @2730',work pipe free,wipe hole 2 times,Run 68 jnts of 13.375",72#,L-80,BUTT casing to a depth of 2925'.
NOTE:Bit#5 was a RRB used for cleaning out cement and no new formation drilled.
ROP dropping due to formation change,POH for tri-cone bit.
Altered Zone @3370',only 10' Serp:lt grn-wht,com pink,med gr-aphan,w/euhed and vng qtz.
Pump 2 down at 3969'. Begin losing 80 bbls/hr while circulating. Pump 60 bbl lcm pills at 3977' and 4003' to cure losses.
Begin losing 35bph@4421'.Lose 400bph initially at cnx when picking up high.Spot LCM pill and circulate losing ~125bph. Pull to shoe to condition mud.
Drill ahead t/4480' w/80bph losses. Set 300' cement plug @4488'.TOC @4203'.Drill ahead with 12.25"bit and mud motor.
Decr WOB @4680'while repair pump#1. 120 SPM for pump#2.

Begin losing 35bph @5071'. Loss rate increases to 300bph @5089'.Lose total circulation @5098' & during cnx @5106'. Set 200' cement plug#2 @5106'. Clean out cement and drill ahead t/5126' with 100bph losses.Set 150' cement plug #3 @5126'.
